    </div>

  </div> <!-- end of navcan -->

  <div id="contentCan">

    <div class="wideBar"></div>

    <div class="contentWide">
      
      <h3 id="chatHeader">Chat</h3>

      <p>This is a very basic chatroom.  You can sign up or log in below.</p>
      <p>I have only tested this chat in Google Chrome and on Windows.  If you experience anything strange, or if certain features do not appear functional, try switching to Chrome.  This is still a work in progress, so expect it to be buggy.</p>
      <p>Please do not include any unusual symbols in your username.  I strip all unusual symbols from usernames, but have not yet created an error message for those of you who think you'll be clever by printing arcane nonsense into your name.  Passwords, however, can probably be whatever you like.  That said, there is no password recovery process yet, so make sure that you remember your information.</p>

      <div id="chatSignUp">Sign Up</div>
      <div id="chatLogIn">Log In</div>
      <div class="clear"></div>

    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="clear"></div>

</div>

